1
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:14,240
So many people.

2
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:15,640
How am I supposed to kill them?

3
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:17,480
Why kill them?

4
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:18,640
Just think about it.

5
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:20,760
You are a spy from the Daye Kingdom.

6
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:22,000
If I want to marry you,

7
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,000
wouldn't I have to silence the witnesses?

8
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:28,200
If so many people join forces,

9
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:30,200
I might not be able to kill them all.

10
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:31,640
You mean to say,

11
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,600
even if I am a spy,

12
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:34,880
you wouldn't despise me?

13
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,040
Of course not.

14
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,720
But the Strategist can't know about this.

15
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,920
If he knew,

16
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,200
he'd definitely mock me for a lifetime.

17
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:43,480
Then what if I have a way

18
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,360
to let you mock Yuwen Liang for a lifetime?

19
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,040
I'm all ears.

20
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:57,040
According to you,

21
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,600
Yu Tong is actually the spy,

22
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,880
and is your Third Princess?

23
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,280
Yes.

24
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:02,640
The Third Princess wasn't satisfied

25
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:04,200
with the Princess Consort our Lord arranged for her.

26
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,320
She ran away to escape the marriage.

27
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,200
Father and daughter have an agreement.

28
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,480
If she can earn merit,

29
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,600
the engagement can be cancelled.

30
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,480
This Little Liang is something else.

31
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,760
Colluding with an enemy princess.

32
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,480
Watch how I deal with him later.

33
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,320
You two,

34
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:16,040
tie yourselves up.

35
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:16,720
Move.

36
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,200
I made you worry

37
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,760
I originally wanted to clear my name

38
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,040
That's why I went up the mountain to catch them

39
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,040
It's okay

40
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,040
As long as you're safe

41
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,040
Actually, I quite like it here

42
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,600
I wish I could stay here forever

43
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,320
Alright then

44
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,480
After the war is over

45
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,800
I'll live here in seclusion with you

46
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,880
Are you really willing to, for my sake

47
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,040
Live in the mountains forever

48
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,040
Of course I am

49
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,720
I think it's quite nice here

50
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,560
Besides

51
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,480
I can eat your cooking every day

52
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,880
It came from practice

53
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,000
Before, when I didn't practice martial arts properly

54
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,840
Master would punish me by making me cook

55
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,000
Your kung fu is so good

56
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,880
And your cooking is so delicious

57
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,360
If I were your Master

58
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,360
I'd punish you to cook every day

59
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,480
Why didn't I think of that

60
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,720
For three whole years

61
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,360
Master punished me every day

62
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,360
I always thought my martial arts were too poor

63
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,760
I didn't expect

64
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,600
He just wanted to eat my cooking

65
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,440
Wait a minute

66
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,600
You just said you trained for how many years

67
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:19,600
Three years

68
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,480
Only three years

69
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,440
And you're already this good

70
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,840
How long have you trained

71
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,800
Me

72
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,360
About three months

73
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,800
Three months

74
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,000
Then you need to work hard

75
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,000
Don't tell anyone

76
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:37,880
What are you talking about

77
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,600
Shoo, shoo

78
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,000
Go

79
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,560
Just drying it like this is enough

80
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,800
No problem

81
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,000
When we are on the march

82
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,000
We always dry them like this

83
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,800
It's easy to preserve

84
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:48,880
What a coincidence

85
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:49,760
Us too

86
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,360
Stand up

87
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,440
Us too

88
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,200
Who let you interrupt

89
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,000
Why are you getting mad at me

90
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,360
The Village Chief let me stay here

91
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,800
Besides

92
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,800
If we get out of here

93
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:01,920
Won't we be family

94
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:02,320
Stop

95
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,600
Squat down

96
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:07,120
Who's family with you

97
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,000
No one in our family looks as pathetic as you

98
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,560
Wait

99
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,200
Let me confirm one more time

100
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,240
Is what you just said true

101
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,560
Absolutely true

102
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,360
From now on, Sister and Brother-in-law

103
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,240
I will follow your lead

104
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,200
Do you know

105
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,480
What to do after we go in

106
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,600
Capture the Third Princess

107
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,680
Strive to redeem myself through merit

108
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:26,880
Let's go

109
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,200
He Qi surrendered too

110
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,320
It's a long story

111
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,440
Caught these two as well

112
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,000
Where is Yu Tong

113
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,800
Tell her to come down

114
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,320
You say I am the Third Princess

115
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,600
Do you have proof?

116
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,880
Do you have proof?

117
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,360
Brother Yuwen

118
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,040
Speak.

119
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,120
I've done everything I can.

120
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:55,560
I don't know why I'm still being targeted.

121
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,200
Then there is only one answer.

122
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,000
The one targeting me is the spy.

123
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:05,440
You!

124
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,000
Silence!

125
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:10,480
Mighty!

126
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,160
What are you fiddling with over there?

127
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,200
Do you even have one to fiddle with?

128
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:13,880
Wei Long.

129
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,800
Let me ask you.

130
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,200
When you arrived,

131
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:18,240
Aqin had already subdued them.

132
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,880
Correct?

133
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,800
Then what if...

134
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,560
Aqin is their leader?

135
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,440
You're talking nonsense!

136
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,680
I clearly caught them!

137
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,920
And they implicated Yu Tong.

138
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,120
What's the point of dwelling on this now?

139
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:34,480
Right?

140
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,440
We can't get out anyway.

141
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:35,880
Right, right, right.

142
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,240
Stop dwelling on it. How is it pointless?

143
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,760
I'm constantly being targeted.

144
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,200
Brother Wei.

145
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,800
Don't let this Aqin deceive you again.

146
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,600
You...

147
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,960
Forget it, Sister Aqin.

148
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,920
Third Princess.

149
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,560
We've figured it out now.

150
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,440
That jar just had some lousy shrimp in it.

151
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,800
Let's just admit it.

152
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,560
Besides,

153
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,200
we can't get out anyway.

154
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,240
Just admit it.

155
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,200
Third Princess.

156
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,040
You're falsely accusing me.

157
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,000
You don't believe me either.

158
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,680
I believe you.

159
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,920
I believe you.

160
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,320
He Qi.

161
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,360
I am the Third Princess, right?

162
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,600
The genuine article.

163
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,800
Good.

164
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,800
Then you do whatever I say.

165
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,680
I'll do anything.

166
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,360
Kill this sorceress for me right now.

167
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,640
Stop!

168
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,560
No fighting allowed.

169
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,240
You hesitated just now.

170
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,680
Yu Tong.

171
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,120
Yu Tong, don't be mad.

172
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:29,200
I will help clear your name.

173
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,120
General Wei keeps suspecting me.

174
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,240
Well, with his intelligence...

175
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,440
suspecting you is normal.

176
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,560
And he is just...

177
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,920
bewitched by that Aqin.

178
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,920
You know?

179
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,040
Yu Tong.

180
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,520
I believe you.

181
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,080
Gentlemen.

182
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,600
I have an announcement.

183
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,880
After deliberation by the village...

184
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,800
He Qi and his two brothers...

185
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,880
each person, every day...

186
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,280
catch five catties of shrimp.

187
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,120
As for you lot...

188
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,360
catch 100 catties of shrimp each day.

189
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,440
Okay.

190
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,600
Why do we have to catch 100 catties?

191
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,840
And they only catch five?

192
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,160
It's obvious.

193
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,400
They were bribed.

194
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,360
Can't you bribe them too?

195
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,760
Then go swap with He Ba.

196
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,720
You'd make even better bait down there.

197
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,320
Forget it, forget it, forget it.

198
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,480
He Qi.

199
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,080
You do our share.

200
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,920
I've joined the village now.

201
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,080
I'm a villager here.

202
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,600
Sorry about that, Third Princess.

203
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,600
Are you my subordinate?

204
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,400
You're my subordinate but won't listen to me?

205
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,080
Unless your boss...

206
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,720
is someone else?

207
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,160
Fine, I...

208
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,600
I'll do it, I'll do it, I'll do it.

209
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,440
Get out of the way.

210
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,240
Useless.

211
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,240
Why are you still squatting there?

212
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,440
Go get to work.

213
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,880
Give me a couple more rubs.
